    <div class="faq-content" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;">

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Pourquoi l'or est-il sacré ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Pour son éclat solaire et son incorruptibilité.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Argent et intuition ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Il favorise l'écoute de soi et des rêves.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Or rose signification ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Romance et tendresse moderne.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Le platine en bijouterie ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Force pure et rareté ultime.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #fcfcfc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #9335B6; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
            <h4 style="color: #9335B6; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600;">Q: Métal et allergies ?</h4>
            <p style="color: #444444; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> L'or pur et le platine sont les plus sûrs.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </main>
        <Footer />
